headline: Aurora to Host Fourth Quarter 2025 Business Review Conference Call on February 11, 2026
summary: PITTSBURGH, January 21, 2026--Aurora Innovation, Inc. (NASDAQ: AUR) today announced it will release fourth quarter 2025 results after market close on February 11, 2026 and will host a business review conference call that day at 5:00 p.m. Eastern time. The conference call will be webcast on Aurora’s investor relations website at ir.aurora.tech. A replay of the webcast will be available for 30 days following the call.
